this type of signaling

00:31:17.870 --> 00:31:22.190
to show the iridescent coloring,
the size of the patterns,

00:31:22.190 --> 00:31:23.570
the size of the tail--

00:31:23.570 --> 00:31:28.160
all of this is what's known
in biology as a handicap

00:31:28.160 --> 00:31:29.210
