and avoiding predators.

00:31:44.040 --> 00:31:46.310
It actually increases
the likelihood

00:31:46.310 --> 00:31:48.290
of a predator seeing him.

00:31:48.290 --> 00:31:49.820
So how could it evolve?

00:31:49.820 --> 00:31:52.400
Through natural selection it
