So it's really interesting
because in your book

01:13:40.160 --> 01:13:42.243
you talked about if you're
driving a high end car,

01:13:42.243 --> 01:13:44.540
people are less likely
to honk when you're

01:13:44.540 --> 01:13:47.180
late at a red light compared to
