01:19:47.820 --> 01:19:50.361
JORDAN THIBODEAU: There seems
to be a push against dissension

01:19:50.361 --> 01:19:51.480
in academia.

01:19:51.480 --> 01:19:54.090
Is this a recent development,
or is this something

01:19:54.090 --> 01:19:57.120
that's been going on since the
