01:20:05.560 --> 01:20:06.910
I really have two hats.

01:20:06.910 --> 01:20:09.640
I both have the
hat of an academic

01:20:09.640 --> 01:20:11.850
who publishes in
journals and so on.

01:20:11.850 --> 01:20:14.760
But I also weigh in on
