on-- is the tentative title

01:20:35.380 --> 01:20:37.650
is "Death of the
West by 1,000 Cuts."

01:20:37.650 --> 01:20:41.522
I go into what has led
us down this quagmire.

01:20:41.522 --> 01:20:43.230
So no, I don't think
it's a recent thing.

01:20:43.230 --> 01:20:45.600
I think it's taken
about 40 years

01:20:45.600 --> 01:20:47.700
of horrifying faux
intellectualism

01:20:47.700 --> 01:20:50.410
to lead us to the
place where we are at.

01:20:50.410 --> 01:20:52.530
And some of these movements,
in case some of you

01:20:52.530 --> 01:20:56.550
want to know, postmodernism,
everything is relative,

01:20:56.550 --> 01:20:58.050
there are no objective truths.

01:20:58.050 --> 01:21:01.410
Cultural and moral
relativism, identity politics,

01:21:01.410 --> 01:21:04.410
intersectionality,
radical feminism-- each

01:21:04.410 --> 01:21:09.750
of these movements are perfect
anti-science, anti-reason

01:21:09.750 --> 01:21:10.830
positions.

01:21:10.830 --> 01:21:13.320
Put them all together,
you get a cocktail.

01:21:13.320 --> 01:21:16.230
You get a melange
of utter nonsense

01:21:16.230 --> 01:21:17.790
that has led us to where we are.

01:21:17.790 --> 01:21:20.520
So I'd like to think
that there's a few of us

01:21:20.520 --> 01:21:25.140
now that are working
to fight against this.

01:21:25.140 --> 01:21:28.290
The news is still not good
because I will often receive

01:21:28.290 --> 01:21:31.870
