01:21:40.610 --> 01:21:43.530
As if supporting
freedom of speech,

01:21:43.530 --> 01:21:45.470
freedom of
intellectual diversity

01:21:45.470 --> 01:21:48.080
is a controversial topic.

01:21:48.080 --> 01:21:51.470
They support freedom
of speech, but they're

01:21:51.470 --> 01:21:53.360
afraid to state so openly.

01:21:53.360 --> 01:21:56.190
So we're in a
difficult position.

01:21:56.190 --> 01:21:58.160
But a few of us are
fighting very hard

01:21:58.160 --> 01:22:00.365
to try to reverse the trend.

